item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Das Ich - Discography FLAC
item.description:
Looking for any and all material by German gothic/industrial band Das Ich, FLAC if possible. Including but not limited to:
  • 1990: Satanische Verse
  • 1991: Die Propheten
  • 1994: Staub
  • 1998: Egodram
  • 1998: Morgue
  • 2002: Anti'christ
  • 2004: LAVA:Glut
  • 2006: Cabaret (limited box set issued featuring remix album Varieté)
    and
  • 2000: Re-Laborat (Remix album)
Cheers!
item.author: fruitmeat
